title: Fantastic Condo! Boca!! Call today! WOWOWOW!
posting_body: ['MUST HAVE STRONG CREDIT!', 'NO EVICTIONS!', 'NO CRIMINAL RECORDS!', 'NO EXCEPTIONS!', 'PLEASE FIND THE EXACT PROPERTY ADDRESS 1/4 INCH UNDER THE MAP IN THE LISTING FOR YOUR REFERENCE!!!!!', 'CALL NOW!!!!!', 'PLEASE FIND THE EXACT PROPERTY ADDRESS 1/4 INCH UNDER THE MAP IN THE LISTING FOR YOUR REFERENCE!!!!!!', 'Email Me, Call Me, or Text!!!!', 'Shawn Kaminsky', 'show contact info', 'Nice 2/2 corner unit in waterfront condominium community located in the heart of beautiful downtown Boca Raton.', 'Main bedroom with walk-in closet, all tile floor throughout, washer/dryer in the unit.', 'Enjoy and relax on the large screened in lanai with partial canal views.', 'The unit is freshly painted.', 'Boca Bayou is an all age community and offers great amenities such as 24-hour manned gate, five pools, grills, boat docks, lighted tennis courts, clubhouse, saunas, shuffleboard, fitness room, onsite management and more.', 'Boca Bayou is very conveniently located only 2 miles from Mizner Park and 4 miles to the beaches.', 'Water, sewer and cable including HBO are included in the rent.', 'One assigned parking spot.', 'Service/ESA pets only with proper documentation.', "Across the street is a park offers a walking trail, basketball hoops, tennis, a children's park, boat and kayak launch.", 'pedestrian walkways, terraced steps/seating, interactive art/play/water features, picnic pavilions and additional parking.']
